
Description
-----------
 - Program deals with 3 cases SIG_DFL,SIG_IGN and registring with a handler.
 - It consists of an alarm, before alarm expires signal SIGINT has default action.
 - After alarm expires SIGINT is ignored. 

Steps to run the program:
-------------------------

 1. make
 It will generate a executable file thread and execute.

 2. ./signal 
 Run executable

 3. make clean
 Removes executable file thread.


OUTPUT
-------

./signal 
 	 Received SIG_ALRM

^C
^C
^C
^C
^\Quit (core dumped)

